    </section>
    <section id="HC8143F74873D418B931B2FD78477332B">
      <enum>6.</enum>
      <header>Relationship to
			 other laws</header>
      <text display-inline="no-display-inline">Nothing in this Act
			 shall be construed to invalidate or limit the remedies, rights, and procedures
			 of any Federal law or law of any State or political subdivision of any State or
			 jurisdiction that provides greater or equal protection for workers affected by
			 pregnancy, childbirth, or related medical conditions.</text>
		</section>
